ooklyn based weaver  erin m  riley has rendered scantily clad selfies into tapestries the possibilities seem endless     i always joke that fiber is my alphabet     says hicks     i can say an unlimited range of things  it can be friendly or aggressive  very sexy or totally pure  it goes from the absolute minimalistic to this intricate  laced  chaotic world    
